### POST /api/v1/admin/tenants
### Descripción: Crear un nuevo tenant. Requiere rol Admin o Support.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TenantDto) | 400 { "error", "code" }

# @name createTenant
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tenants
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi Tenant"
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "id": "guid",
#   "name": "string",
#   "isActive": true,
#   "createdAtUtc": "2025-03-02T12:00:00Z"
# }

### Response error (400):
# {
#   "error": "string",
#   "code": "string"
# }
